com.zhuinden.simplestack.navigator

Class DefaultStateChanger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zhuinden.simplestack.navigator.DefaultStateChanger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StateChanger

    public final class DefaultStateChanger
extends java.lang.Object
implements StateChanger
    A default state changer that handles view changes, and allows an optional external state changer (which is executed before the view change). For the default behavior to work, all keys must implement StateKey, which specifies a layout, and a ViewChangeHandler. But if DefaultStateChanger.LayoutInflationStrategy and DefaultStateChanger.GetViewChangeHandlerStrategy are re-defined, then this is no longer necessary.
